snippet.title: News!!! Mattel Amber Collection in stores! Grab'N'Go Rebor Rex Paint Schemes!!!
snippet.description:
Today we have news on the Mattel Amber Collection in stores! Images of the full Raptor Snap Squad set! Rebor's Grab'N'Go T. Rex figures paint schemes! Info on Rebor's King Trident! A bunch of new Beasts of the Mesozoic Prototypes including the painted Diabloceratops! Dino Dreams new "Charlie" Velociraptor! A new Kaiyodo T. Rex kit! New Masterpiece Models 1/15 scale kits coming soon! 

Music Created by Cloudmeister!! Credit goes to them! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bdDPjXbAZzo
